name: I'll Quit Being a God
summary: The sky and the earth are infinitesimal as a grain, and a life of peace is like the sea.Lu Heng, who crossed over to the other world, found himself transformed into a huge white wolf, a mountain God of a remote mountain with a group of villagers under his rule.In this strange and wild world, demons and giant beasts run rampant, and human order is almost non-existent.These, however, are not what Lu Heng needs to think about. What he needs to think about now is how to tell this group of villagers that he does not need little girls.Besides, he actually doesn’t want to be a God anymore…
author: July Wine Immortal
